# AI Agent Instructions for Orbit Monorepo

This document contains all AI-relevant information for working with the Orbit monorepo. It consolidates instructions, patterns, conventions, and best practices to help AI agents understand and work effectively with this codebase.

## Table of Contents

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Nx Workspace Guidelines](#nx-workspace-guidelines)
- [Project Structure](#project-structure)
- [Key Workflows](#key-workflows)
