## Key Workflows

### Installation & Setup

```bash
# Install all dependencies
pnpm i

# Install Playwright browsers (for E2E tests)
pnpm exec playwright install
```

### Development

```bash
# Run dev server for a specific app
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:dev

# Or for other apps
pnpm nx run @dtc/spotlight.rms.rocks:dev
```

### Building

```bash
# Build all projects
pnpm build:all

# Build affected projects
pnpm build:affected

# Build specific project
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:build
```

### Testing

```bash
# Unit tests - all
pnpm test:unit:all

# Unit tests - affected
pnpm test:unit:affected

# Unit tests - specific project
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:unit

# Unit tests - UI mode (in any app/lib directory)
pnpm test:unit:ui

# E2E tests - all
pnpm test:e2e:all

# E2E tests - affected
pnpm test:e2e:affected

# E2E tests - specific app
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e

# E2E tests - UI mode
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e --ui

# E2E tests - show report
pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e show-report
```

### Code Quality

```bash
# Lint all
pnpm lint:all

# Format all
pnpm format:all

# Typecheck all
pnpm typecheck:all

# Check all
pnpm check:all
```

### Dependency Graph

```bash
# View dependency graph
pnpm nx graph

# View affected graph
pnpm nx affected:graph
```

### Maintenance

```bash
# Update icon types
pnpm icons:update

# Update design tokens for all projects
pnpm tokens:update:all

# Prune lockfiles
pnpm prune:lockfiles

# Prune node_modules
pnpm prune:node_modules

# Prune Nx cache
pnpm prune:nx
```

