## Testing Guidelines

### Unit Testing (Vitest)

- **Framework:** Vitest (vite-native testing framework)
- **Location:** Colocated with source or in `libs/`
- **Run all:** `pnpm test:unit:all`
- **Run affected:** `pnpm nx affected -t test:unit`
- **Run specific:** `pnpm nx run-many -t test:unit -p @dtc/[project] --parallel=5`
- **UI mode:** `pnpm test:unit:ui` (in any app/lib directory)
- **Update snapshots:** `pnpm test:unit:all:update`

### E2E Testing (Playwright)

- **Framework:** Playwright
- **Location:** `apps/<app>/e2e/` or in `libs/`
- **Patterns:**
  - Use custom viewports
  - Mock external resources for stability
  - Mock images and video requests to avoid flakiness
  - Some tests require credentials from app config (`features.basicAuthentication.credentials`)
  - Some tests skip certain apps via a blacklist array
- **Run specific app:** `pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e`
- **UI mode:** `pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e --ui`
- **Show report:** `pnpm nx run @dtc/orbit.rms.rocks:test:e2e show-report`

### Visual Regression Testing

- **Tool:** Chromatic
- **Project:** [Chromatic Builds](https://www.chromatic.com/build?appId=667c16908487868c8374ad55)
- **Trigger:** Manual dispatch via GitHub Action workflow

**Local execution:**

```bash
# Install browsers
pnpm exec playwright install

# Build and start spotlight
pnpm nx run @dtc/spotlight.rms.rocks:build && pnpm nx run @dtc/spotlight.rms.rocks:start

# Run against localhost
TARGET_URL=https://localhost:3333 pnpm nx run @dtc/spotlight.rms.rocks:test:visual:local

# Run against published version
pnpm nx run @dtc/spotlight.rms.rocks:test:visual:local
```

